    <h1>You were born under <em>two skies</em>. This is how they cross.</h1>
    <p class="lede">The Primal Animal is what you get when your Western Sun sign meets your Chinese year animal. This page explains where the figure comes from, why the Moon runs through all of it, and why the reading describes meaning rather than predicting the future.</p>
